OL,3,CUK Illegal Migration Act should be
OL,4,Cdisapplied in NI, judge rules
OL,6,FA judge has ruled that provisions of
OL,7,Fthe UK's Illegal Migration Act should
OL,8,Fbe disapplied in Northern Ireland, as
OL,9,Fthey undermine human rights
OL,10,Fprotections guaranteed in the region
OL,11,Funder post-Brexit arrangements.
OL,13,FMr Justice Humphreys also said aspects
OL,14,Fof the Act were incompatible with the
OL,15,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights
OL,16,F(ECHR).
