OL,3,CUK Illegal Migration Act should be
OL,4,Cdisapplied in NI, judge rules
OL,6,FThe post-Brexit Windsor Framework
OL,7,Fjointly agreed by the UK and EU
OL,8,Fincludes a stipulation that there can
OL,9,Fbe no diminution of the rights
OL,10,Fprovisions contained within Northern
OL,11,FIreland's Good Friday peace agreement
OL,12,Fof 1998.
OL,14,FThe Illegal Migration Act provides new
OL,15,Fpowers for the Government to detain
OL,16,Fand remove asylum seekers it deems to
OL,17,Fhave arrived illegally in the UK.
OL,19,FCentral to the new laws is the scheme
OL,20,Fto send asylum seekers to Rwanda.
