OL,3,CUK Illegal Migration Act should be
OL,4,Cdisapplied in NI, judge rules
OL,6,FMr Justice Humphreys delivered
OL,7,Fjudgment at Belfast High Court on
OL,8,FMonday in two challenges against the
OL,9,FAct that focused on the peace process
OL,10,Fhuman rights protections guaranteed by
OL,11,Fthe Windsor Framework.
OL,13,FThe judge found that several elements
OL,14,Fof the Act do cause a "significant"
OL,15,Fdiminution of the rights enjoyed by
OL,16,Fasylum seekers residing in Northern
OL,17,FIreland under the terms of the Good
OL,18,FFriday Agreement.
