OL,6,F"We'll be taking our instructions on
OL,7,Fthe judgment and the position in terms
OL,8,Fof any further litigation will become
OL,9,Fclear, my Lord," he said.
OL,11,FOutside court, solicitor Sinead
OL,12,FMarmion, who represented the teenage
OL,13,FIranian asylum seeker applicant, said
OL,14,Fthe judgment was "hugely significant".
OL,16,FMs Marmion said the judgment would
OL,17,Fprevent the Rwanda scheme applying in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland.
